KASSL EDITIONS X ZARA collection
Whether expressed in the perfect nylon rain hat or a quilted sofa, KASSL’s preoccupations with tactility, longevity, quality and colour are apparent 
in every item in the KASSL EDITIONS X ZARA capsule collection. 
The ambitious collaboration typifes KASSL’s distinctive clean, unpolished aesthetic and the brand’s commitment to quality.
#kassleditionsxzara @kassleditions

KASSL EDITIONS X ZARA collection
From early September 2021, individuals everywhere have a special opportunity to fully immerse themselves in the exacting inner and outer worlds of KASSL Editions, as the cult label adored by fashion insiders for its desirable utility-wear proudly presents a collection of durable objects for the home and an edit of new ready-to-wear designs with the respected brand Zara.
#kassleditionsxzara @kassleditions

KASSL EDITIONS X ZARA collection.
Modern, modular dressing for the home and the individual

JOIN LIFE. We are working to make both our physical and online stores increasingly more sustainable. To this end, we are developing specific programs to design, build and manage our stores efficiently and with a lower environmental impact. Our goal is that by 2022, 10% of the energy in all our headquarters logistics centres and stores will come from renewable sources 
#JOINLIFE

JOIN LIFE. Under the label Join Life we categorize all garments that have been produced using processes and raw materials that help us reduce our environmental impact. Our goal is that by 2022, 50% of our products will meet our Join Life standard.  
#JOINLIFE

JOIN LIFE. Working towards sustainability. 

At Zara, we understand sustainability as an ongoing effort. We develop specific programs from a holistic approach. Emphasizing social and environmental sustainability and the safety and health of our products. 
#JOINLIFE
